                  <span class="text-slate-300">AI-first approach to learning management systems</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-center space-x-3">
                  <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-blue-400 rounded-full"></div>
                  <span class="text-slate-300">Experienced team with proven EdTech track record</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-center space-x-3">
                  <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-blue-400 rounded-full"></div>
